<p class="canvas-note"><strong>Ghost Traffic</strong> — A dense stream of amber particles flows at machine speed. Four off-white gates hold the stream briefly at human decision points. Over the cycle, the gates grow dim and the pauses shorten until the stream flows unbroken. The checkpoints were always optional.</p>

<section class="section" id="trust-me">
  <h2><span class="num">02 — Trust Me</span>What Anthropic Didn't Publish</h2>
  <p>The report omitted indicators of compromise. No IP addresses. No domain names. No file hashes. No YARA rules. No infrastructure analysis. No attribution methodology. No jailbreak prompts.</p>

  <div class="aice-report-wrap">
    <div class="aice-report-col">
